filter.description: Return only usages specified in the filter. Filter is specified by using OData syntax. Example: $filter=(name.value eq 'Metric1' or name.value eq 'Metric2') and startTime eq '2014-01-01T00:00:00Z' and endTime eq '2014-12-31T23:59:59Z' and timeGrain eq duration'[Hour|Minute|Day]'.
